---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
import ContentSection from "~/components/content-section.astro";
---

<ContentSection title="Meet your new team member." id="intro">
  <Fragment slot="lead">
    Hiring a developer is
    <span class="text-primary">hard</span> and
    <span class="text-primary">expensive.</span>
    Extensibl Media <span class="text-primary">solves</span> this with a subscription access to developer resources at a <span class="text-primary">reasonable</span> cost.
  </Fragment>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
    <a
      href="/our-process"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 border-2 border-current px-6 py-4"
    >
      <Icon pack="mdi" name="magnify" class="h-8" />
      <span>Learn More</span>
    </a>
    <a
      href="#contact-us"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 border-2 border-current px-6 py-4"
    >
      <Icon pack="mdi" name="rocket" class="h-8" />
      <span>Get Started</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</ContentSection>
